# The published tarball ships: the built CLI + library + types (dist/), the attack corpus
# (attacks/), and the policy pack. TypeScript source is NOT shipped — the library entry is the
# built dist/index.js + dist/index.d.ts. (With this file present, npm ignores .gitignore, so
# dist/ IS published even though .gitignore lists it.)

